                     <interp inst="t18310908-72-person681" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I live in Asbby-street, St. Johnstreet-road, and am a builder. The prisoner has been my groom and labourer more than five years and a half; this property was kept in a secure place, and the prisoner obtained the key of the drop-latch to get in there.</p>
